urls.title: GOTV Rally with AOC, Bernie Sanders & Jamaal Bowman Â· Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez for Congress
urls.description: Join Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, Bernie Sanders, and Jamaal Bowman for a rally and canvass kick-off on the weekend before the Democratic Primary! We will have guest speakers, performances, and volunteers will have the option of canvassing door-to-door for AOC, doing poll site visibility at a local early voting site, or bussing into NY-16 to canvass for Jamaal Bowman. Voting Info: https://www.ocasiocortez.com/vote
